 Latest from the readme file :

README

My goal is to start writing and using Mentor. Right now the development
is practically halted because too much is on my head.



DESIGN
The basic initial design
Basically it will be a replacement for my SMEX program in Delphi - with
another syntax (xml-based) and helper macros in VIM/Python.


1. Creating data
Data will be stored in XML format and edited in VIM.
I will have python macros which will help me convert raw data into
meaningul items which can be later memorized.


2. Memorization
Memorization will be done in SuperMemo.
Right now I don't have time nor motivation to start coding at full
repetition GUI.

3. Databases
I have to create and use some databases in order to get in full motion.
Then I can think of even more improvements

Home:
Welcome to Mentor

MENTOR is a tool for improving the learning process.


It can be used as a help in learning foreign languages , geography , science and
can be used everywhere, where there is a need to comprehend knowledge and
somehow memorize it and keep it in memory .


knowledge may be split into seperate items which can be memorized.

By learning process is meant extracting knowledge from written material,
processing it to more consumable form and then memorizing it and storing in
memory.

MENTOR helps by providing ways of extracting knowledge (by summarizing ) and
transforming it (emacs macros) to flashcards




MENU:
Home
News
Downloads
