.#12 How to go about comments? 16:05 ([[2007.10.11#8]])
  Put % (\% escaped)
  1. remove text from comments
  2. put all text which is not in { } as default class
  3. the default class may be specified via command line option or setting in
  .probe file or \defaultclass{set} setting
   --> first must search for the default class
   default=set[swap]

  In default mode all is treated as set class

  If in strict mode all needs to b
Invalid character found !
% at the beginning of line
\%
  %% to comment line
  %%

